Employee 3rd Anniversary Balloons Card

Review Employee 3rd Anniversary Balloons Card – Anniversary Cards Popular Employee 3rd Anniversary Balloons Card if you are looking for it, we recommend it Employee 3rd Anniversary Balloons Card You can read more about itThis is an employee 3rd anniversary card design in the style of digital scrapbooking. The design features five colorful balloons which have been drawn in a fun, freehand style. In addition, there are two labels lower down with thread effect detail where the number of years and ‘Happy Anniversary’ are written in black in a typewriter style font. There are also some celebratory scattered stars over the labels and the balloons.

PLEASE NOTE: All gold foil and 3D effects are simulated within the artwork, no gold foil or 3D elements will be used in the making of this card. The card will be a completely flat print.

Design by Natalie Kinnear Price:$4.42
